New core motion pillars
Metamorphic Continuity
Forms should transform continuously into adjacent symbolic states rather than cutting cleanly
between unrelated states.

Hidden-Form Revelation
Animation should feel like one image contains the seed of the next image.

Symbolic Substitution
Movement is often identity change, not physical travel.

Looped Dream Recurrence
Cycles feel trance-like, recursive, and slightly cheap in a good way.

Elastic Contour Logic
Outlines bend, stretch, and redistribute mass while preserving a loose family resemblance.

Pattern-Figure Permeability
Abstract fields and cartoon beings can mutate into each other.

